{"tid":1109380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"土瓜灣碼頭82歲老翁墮海 送院不治","createTime":"2019-04-16T09:06:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T09:14:12.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e9f001e87a07943ab892a14e576ba099bb1ea2c1","tid":1109380,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T09:06:27.000Z","msg":"土瓜灣馬頭角公眾碼頭發現男子墮海。上午9時許，有市民報案指發現一名身穿灰色上衣的男子，在海中載浮載沉，警方及消防員接報到場救援，發現一名老翁於岸邊樓梯位底部位置，老翁被救起時昏迷，送往伊利沙伯醫院搶救後證實不治。警員經調查後獲悉老翁姓姚（82歲），並在岸邊發現他的袋及一把雨遮，列作有人墮海處理，警方正調查事件。據了解，事主有身體病患。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」： <a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=Gknyi0oE%2F3XF1rBdSl6%2FM4TtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=57407ae9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190416/59493723\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190416%2F59493723&d=Gknyi0oE%2F3XF1rBdSl6%2FM4TtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=e3349290\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190416%2F59493723&h=34afcb61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190416/59493723</a>"},{"pid":"ebd5faeadcc5a2f8f82287181e6c0cfbe9f072f1","tid":1109380,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T09:07:10.000Z","msg":"廢老-1<br />\n口德-1"},{"pid":"d98f79dcbc27f9349421a018aacc479d39e74cc3","tid":1109380,"uid":36673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T09:14:12.000Z","msg":"Rip <br />\n日常1/1 點解香港無安樂死"}]}